    dc:title "Descriptions of three new species and one subspecies of Physatocheila (Heteroptera: Tingidae) from China and the Russian Far East, with an identification key to the species of the Russian fauna" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10135777>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10135773>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10135775>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10135781>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10135783>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10135785> ;
